Seattle, WA, based Investment company Merriman Wealth Management, LLC buys Schwab U.S. Broad Market, iShares 20+ Year Treasury Bond ETF, SPDR S&P Regional Banking, Schwab International Small-Cap Equity, SPDR DJ Wilshire REIT, SPDR DJ Wilshire Intl Real Estate, iShares U.S. Broker-Dealers & Securities Exchanges, SPDR S&P Metals & Mining, Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets, Apache, sells SPDR S&P Oil & Gas Explor & Product, PACCAR, Vanguard Small-Cap Value ETF - DNQ, iShares S&P Mid-Cap 400 Value, iShares Core S&P 500 during the 3-months ended 2017-03-31, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Merriman Wealth Management, LLC. As of 2017-03-31, Merriman Wealth Management, LLC owns 121 stocks with a total value of $388 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: SCHB, RWR, RWX, IAI, HYEM, RSX, DATA, AIA, ILF, XLK, Added Positions: TLT, KRE, SCHC, XME, VWO, APA, SPY, WY, VOD, ELLI, Reduced Positions: XOP, AMGN, VBR, IVV, HL, QQQ, DEO, SCHO, USB, T, Sold Out: PCAR, IJJ, AMZN, GM, IJK, CWB, AMLP, JNK, HYG, PCEF, 
